  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400 degrees Fahrenheit).",
    "Thread lamb loin chops onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, ginger, salt, black pepper, paprika, and red pepper flakes.",
    "Brush the mixture evenly onto both sides of the lamb kebabs.",
    "Place the kebabs on the grill and cook for 4-5 minutes per side, or until they reach an internal temperature of 145 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Transfer the kebabs to a plate and let them rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle with chopped parsley and sumac before serving"
